 additional insight into the role\nplayed by the competitive adsorption of the counterions and polyelectrolytes on\nthe surfaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Sep 2012 23:35:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-02"}
