ng on the basal and prismatic planes and the\nalloy showed similar strengthening against basal slip to Mg-Zn. The elongation\nincreased linearly with particle spacing. The ductility of Mg-Zn-Y alloys was\nsimilar to that of Mg-Zn for equivalently spaced particles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 29 Sep 2012 05:15:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-06"}
